{"tid":2088951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔一名黑衣男突然墮樓受傷 黑警稱會拘捕該男子","createTime":"2020-07-01T12:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T12:45:24.000Z","uid":22556,"like":44,"dislike":179,"uniUserReply":141,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab10d2aba70f7af1f1178732db9602e569d7d61","tid":2088951,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"【 7.1｜灣仔黑衣人墮樓  獲消防救出後被捕 】<br />\n <br />\n晚上7:30，灣仔明豐大廈有一名身穿黑衣市民懷疑墮樓，倒臥簷篷上。消防到場救出黑衣男子，將其送上救護車後離開。現場一帶被警方包圍，現場警察指將會拘捕該名男子。<br />\n<br />\n據現場目擊人士稱黑衣男最初因為逃避未知人士追趕因而失足，由高處跌落簷蓬。<br />\n<br />\n攝 Photo : Billy Choy, Ivan Ng, Long Tse<br />\n撰 Edit ：Angus Wong<br />\n<br />\n#flashmediahongkong #fmhk #flashmediahk #hkmedia #2020 <br />\n<br />\nLike同Share本媒專頁Flash Media Hong Kong (FMHK) 以獲取更多新聞資訊和社會報導。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/flashmediahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fflashmediahk%2F&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=cdb1ffe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/flashmediahk/</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: @flashmediahk<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112467260231947/posts/180726500072689/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112467260231947%2Fposts%2F180726500072689%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=500f2229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112467260231947/posts/180726500072689/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a5af7ef71c94e08f341e6bb97ee233b4c06189b9","tid":2088951,"uid":24457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d429732933a5ba62706bf762a23f41af4df947","tid":2088951,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal